report.title: Getting Tarded
report.author: Anonymous Lucky Guy
report.bodytext: T+0:35 /n First rushes, very nice and warm /n /n T+0:40 /n Feeling lighter then air, floating physically and mentally /n /n T+0:46 /n Bowels loosen, go to empty them, its unusually enjoyable /n /n T+0:47 /n As I stand, the Belch, the taste all these beta ketone amphetamine analogs seem to have /n /n T+0:51 /n I notice how restless I am /n /n T+1:02 /n E-tard grin zoom a zoom a zoom zoom zoom. Fairly slow come up, end up with a happy glow. Just a bit of 'engine revving' /n /n T+2:08 /n The last hour has been a unremarkable, slightly altered, but its already petering out /n /n Typical entactogen enhancements, but not very pronounced. Nothing noteworthy to report after that. Tapers off after another 90 min or so to baseline.
